        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1, <strong>wearisome</strong>(令人疲倦的)</p><p>eg: Simple repetitive tasks can be wearisome most of the time.</p><p>2,<strong>expedition</strong></p><p>eg:The building is partly a museum and partly a private residence.(住宅)</p><p>3,<strong>warden</strong> (看守人)</p><p>4,<strong>gasp</strong>(急促的呼吸)</p><p>eg:Mary climbed slowly ,gasping for breath.</p><p>5,<strong>stretch</strong> </p><p>eg:I learn back in the chair and stetched.(伸展肢体)</p><p>6,<strong>hemmed in</strong>(被包围)</p><p>eg:hemmed in by the enemy</p><p>7,****</p>]]></content>
      
      
